cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is primarily focused on deep face recognition and reducing racial bias in biometric systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a deep unsupervised domain adaptation method, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI). Additionally, the paper uses datasets and evaluates the performance of the proposed method, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the issue of bias in biometric systems, which can be considered a security and privacy concern (cs.CR).
